My Ad is performong really badly, I got 3 installs for 120 dollars costs

I'm sorry to hear that your ad is not performing well. To help improve your ad performance, could you please let me know which bidding strategy you are currently using? For example, are you using Max Conversions, Target CPA, or another strategy? This information will help me provide more specific guidance.
Howa can I improve the performance&

To improve the performance of your ad, you can try the following strategies:
1. **Adjust Your Bidding Strategy**: If you're using Max Conversions, consider switching to Target CPA bidding to help control costs. If your actual CPA exceeds your expected CPA, decrease the budget first and make sure the performance is under control.
2. **Optimize Your Creative**: Boost your CTR by optimizing your ad creative. A/B testing different creatives can help identify what works best for your audience.
3. **Adjust Your Target Audience**: Make sure you are targeting the right audience for your ad. Adjusting demographics, interests, and behaviors can help improve performance.
4. **Monitor Daily**: Check in on your campaign's performance every day to make necessary adjustments promptly.
For more detailed guidance, you can refer to our Reporting Guide [here](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/18088532505485-Reporting-Guide) and Maximize Conversions Best Practices [here](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/23055076590221-Maximize-Conversions-Best-Practices).
